The APU Administration Office is located at
Level 4, APU New Campus, Technology Park Malaysia, 57000 Kuala Lumpur, Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur.
The operating hours of the Level 4 Admin Office are as below; 
 Monday - Thursday: 
 8:30am - 8pm
 Friday: 8:30am - 7:30pm.
 The Level 4 Admin Office can be contacted via telephone or via email. 
 The general line of the Admin Office is 0389925250.
 The Assignment Submission Counter abides by the operating hours of the Level 4 Admin Office.
  Weekdays: 08:30 AM - 7 pm.
